Getting There:
The plaza is at the corner of West Peachtree St and Ponce de Leon Ave and is on top of the North Avenue MARTA station, so MARTA is a great way to get to the event. There is also abundant paid parking in the vicinity, such as street parking on West Peachtree St, a surface lot next to the station, and the Element and Courtyard hotel parking lot.

